# TC36 : ObstacleDetectedBoost3
# Related normal-mode case : TC26_ObstacleDetected3
# Precondition : BoostMode, forward=false
# Action : left obstacle detected, front/right clear
# Expected : BoostMode 유지, CleanerDriver mode=boost 유지, turnRight, forward=true
power
start
dust
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
obstacle 1 1 1
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motorForward false
obstacle 0 1 0
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
expect motorForward true
expect motorDirection RIGHT
exit
